#: temp.glade:12475 temp.glade:12500
msgid "Some (rare) PDF line-art images do not set \n"
"the colour of their lines, relying instead on \n"
"the 'default' colour, which is normally black. \n"
"This control sets the default colour to something \n"
"other than black, and thus such images can be\n"
"recoloured with this option. If (as most PDF images \n"
"do) the image defines its own colour, this option \n"
"will have no visible effect at all. It is also possible\n"
"that an image will *partly* contain colour information, \n"
"but only starting part way through the file, a situation \n"
"that might produce unexpected results."
msgstr "Sampela (wanpela) PDF line-art piksa i no save putim kala bilong ol lain bilong ol, ol i save putim kala bilong ol long default kala, em i blakpela. Dispela kontrol i putim default kala long narapela kala, na olsem na ol piksa i ken kamap nupela wantaim dispela opsen. Sapos (olsem planti PDF piksa i save mekim) piksa i makim kala bilong em yet, dispela opsen bai no gat wanpela samting i stap. Na tu, inap kamap olsem wanpela piksa i gat sampela tok bilong kala, tasol ol i kirap long hap tasol bilong dispela piksa, na dispela inap kamapim sampela samting yu no bin ting bai kamap."

