#: temp.glade:17941
msgid "Fine Tune Line Spacing:\n\n"
"This button is only active when PTXprint has a suggestion to\n"
"shrink or expand the line spacing slightly to minimise wasted \n"
"vertical space on the page. Click to accept the suggestion.\n\n"
"If there is more than half a line of 'spare' space on the \n"
"page then the line-spacing will decrease slightly to\n"
"fit one more line of text on the page.\n\n"
"If there is less than half a line of 'spare' space on the \n"
"page then the line-spacing will increase slightly to \n"
"fill the page more evenly (with the same number of \n"
"lines of text).\n\n"
"If you prefer to keep the exact line spacing specified, \n"
"then do NOT click this option. Instead, use the similar\n"
"button to adjust either the Top or Bottom Margin."
msgstr "Fine Tune Line Spacing: Dispela boten i save wok taim PTXprint i gat wanpela toksave long liklik liklik o opim liklik hap bilong ol lain i stap namel long ol lain bilong daunim liklik hap bilong ol lain i no gat hap long pes. Klik long orait long toksave. Sapos i gat moa long hap hap bilong ol lain i stap namel long ol lain, orait dispela lain bai go daun liklik na inapim wanpela lain moa bilong ol lain i stap insait long pes. Sapos i gat liklik hap hap tasol bilong hap bilong ol lain i stap long pes, orait dispela hap hap bai i go antap liklik na bai pes i pulap gut (ol wankain lain bilong ol lain i stap long pes). Sapos yu laik holim stret hap hap bilong ol lain i stap, orait NO ken klikim dispela opsen."

