msgstr "Lukim mak bilong Base Font Size na Base Line Spacing olsem spacing i kamap bikpela/i go liklik long size bilong fon; o font size i senis taim spacing i senis."

#: temp.glade:18024
msgid "The space by which paragraphs\n"
"should be indented (inches). This \n"
"also affects poetry indentation.\n"
"Note that for a single-column text\n"
"this value needs to be higher than\n"
"for two-column texts, and the value\n"
"updates automatically when you change\n"
"from 1 to 2 columns, and vice versa. "
msgstr "Dispela hap hap i gat mak bilong ol paragraf i mas i stap insait long en (ins). Dispela i save mekim sampela samting long ol tok bilong ol rait. Tingim olsem long ol tok i gat wanpela kolom tasol, dispela mak i mas i go antap moa long ol tok i gat tupela kolom, na taim yu senisim kolom long 1 na 2 na narapela kolom i go antap, dispela mak bai senis. "

