"also slow down the production of the PDF.\n\n"
"If using this feature, it is recommended to\n"
"also enable option: 'Show Localized Terms Only'."
msgstr "Sapos lista bilong ol tok bilong Baibel i gat ol tok bilong Baibel, orait yu inap soim ol namba bilong Strong long ol tok bilong Baibel yet, na dispela bai helpim yu long painim ol tok i stret long Baibel bilong stadi long en."

