msgstr "Sapos yu laik putim ol tok bilong Baibel long buk bilong yu, yu mas putim namba bilong pes long hap daunbilo bilong buk. Sapos yu laik putim namba bilong pes long hap daunbilo bilong buk bilong yu, yu ken putim namba bilong pes long hap daunbilo bilong buk. Olsem: [\\page number] i putim hap hap bilong sait DRAFT\\ \\isodate\\ \\hrsmins bai givim \"DRAFT YYYY-MM-YY HH:MM\" -empty- i no putim wanpela hap long dispela ples Tingim olsem sapos yu mas i gat Inner/Outer Footers, yu ken putim ol dispela long file ptxprint-mods.tex."

