#: temp.glade:29247
msgid "Is it clear what is happening in this image?"
msgstr "Yu save long samting i kamap long dispela piksa?"

#: temp.glade:29258
msgid "First consider whether this picture is appropriate and culturally acceptable in any publications for this project."
msgstr "Pastaim skelim olsem dispela piksa i stret o nogat long ol buk na nius bilong dispela wok."

#: temp.glade:29260
