msgstr "Dispela piksa i kamapim sampela tok em i no ken kamapim long dispela hap?"

#: temp.glade:29423
msgid "Do the images and their style fit with the type of publication, i.e. Scripture, children’s materials, lectionary, etc.? Are people and actions depicted in acceptable ways?"
msgstr "Ol piksa na pasin bilong ol i stret wantaim ol tok bilong buk, olsem Baibel, ol buk bilong ol pikinini, ol buk bilong skulim ol pikinini, na ol narapela samting?"

#: temp.glade:29425
msgid "Is the image appropriate for the publication?"
msgstr "Dispela piksa i stret long dispela nius?"

