"3. Where they help the reader to understand the passage.\n"
"4. Where it entices the reader to read the passage."
msgstr "Ol i save yusim ol piksa long ol samting olsem: 1. Ol man i no save long ol samting i kamap long skin bilong ol, o ol i no save long ol samting i kamap long skin bilong ol. 2. Ol samting i kamap long skin i bikpela samting long save long mining bilong tok (olsem, kain klos i no bikpela samting, tasol sampela hap tok inap helpim man long kliagut long tok.) 3. Ol i helpim man i ritim long kliagut long tok. 4. Ol i kirapim man long ritim tok."

