"will be disabled. So it is recommended to use \\toc3 as your thumbtab text \n"
"and include it in the Table of Contents. "
msgstr "Long default, ol Thumb Tabs i save yusim ol tok insait na stiles bilong maker \\toc3. Tingim olsem dispela sait i pas wantaim ol samting bilong Table of Contents long Tab Peripherals. Sapos \\toc3 i no stap insait long ToC, orait dispela opsen bai no stap. Olsem na yu mas yusim \\toc3 olsem ol tok insait long thumbtab na putim long Table of Contents. "

#: temp.glade:31127
msgid "\\zthumbtab"
msgstr "Toktok wantaim ol narapela"

#: temp.glade:31132
msgid "By default, Thumb Tabs use the content and styling of the \\toc3 marker.\n"
"If you prefer different content and/or styling for the tabs, then this\n"
"\\zthumbtab option needs to be enabled, and the thumbtab names\n"
"entered into your USFM text.\n\n"
"Note that this setting is interconnected with the Table of Contents settings \n"
"on the Pheripherals tab. If \\toc3 is not included in the ToC, then you are \n"
"forced to use the \\zthumbtab setting here. For that reason it is highly \n"
"recommended to use \\toc3 as your thumbtab text and include it in \n"
"the Table of Contents. \n\n"
"The USFM extension \\zthumbtab'' can be used to set an alternative value for \n"
"the thumbtab contents. If a book's header contains a \\zthumbtab entry, then \n"
"\\toc3 will not be used as the thumbtab contents. An empty \\zthumbtab'' entry \n"
"specifies that there should be no text in the thumbtab for that book."
msgstr "Sapos yu laikim narapela kain ol tok insait na/o stiles bilong ol tab, orait yu mas optimim dispela opsen, na putim ol nem bilong ol thumbtab insait long ol tok bilong yu long USFM. Tingim olsem dispela sait i pas wantaim ol sait bilong ol tok insait long Tabel bilong ol samting i stap long Tab Peripheral. Sapos yu no putim tok insait long ToC, orait yu mas yusim sait bilong \\zthumbtab hia. Olsem na yu mas yusim \\toc3 olsem ol tok bilong yu long ol liklik liklik hap bilong buk na putim long ol tok i stap insait long ol dispela hap. Yu ken yusim USFM estensen \\zthumbtab'' long putim narapela valua bilong ol liklik hap bilong buk. Sapos het bilong buk i gat wanpela tok i stap long ol liklik hap bilong buk, orait yu no ken yusim \\toc3."

