#: temp.glade:35883
msgid "To balance columns of text on a page it is possible\n"
"to specify paragraphs adjustments (shrink or expand):\n\n"
"A Paragraph Adjust List needs to be in this format:\n"
"MRK 2.7 +1    (i.e. expand the para at Mark 2.7 by one line) \n"
"MRK 3.20 -1   (i.e. shrink the para at Mark 3:20 by one line)\n"
"%MARK 4.14 +1   (ignore this line - treat it as a comment)   \n"
"MRK 5.8 +2    (i.e. expand the para at Mark 5.8 by two lines)\n"
"MRK 6.23 +1[2]  (expand the paragraph AFTER the paragraph \n"
"                              which contains MRK 6.23 e.g. a heading.)\n\n"
"Diglot AdjList also need R or L to be specified after the book code\n"
"and it is important that L comes before R for the same verse.\n"
"MATL 3.4 +1\n"
"MATR 3.4 -1\n"
"MATR 3.11 +2\n\n"
"Keyboard Shortcuts:\n"
"  Ctrl-1 - makes the current line +1\n"
"  Ctrl-2 - makes the 2nd para of current line +1[2]\n"
"    ... etc ...\n"
"  Ctrl-9 - makes the 9th para of current line +1[9]\n\n"
"  Ctrl-I - shrink current line -1\n"
"  Ctrl-Grave - ` same as above\n\n"
"  Ctrl-0 - % Comment (or uncomment) the line [it toggles]\n"
"  Ctrl-Comma - same as above\n\n"
"  Ctrl-D - Duplicate the current line\n"
"  Ctlr-L - deLete the current line\n"
"  Ctrl-Up - move the current line up one line\n"
"  Ctrl-Down - move the current line down one line\n\n"
"Note that adjusting paragraphs needs to be done right at the\n"
"end when all other settings have been finalized. Otherwise you\n"
"are likely to have to re-do it all again."
msgstr "Bilong stretim ol kolon bilong ol tok long pes, yu ken makim ol senis long ol paragraf (slim o skruim): Ol lain i mas kamapim ol senis long ol paragraf olsem: MRK 2.7 +1 (em i olsem, skruim wanpela lain long paragraf long Mak 2.7) MRK 3.20 -1 (em i olsem, skruim wanpela lain long paragraf long Mak 3.20) %MARK 4.14 +1 (no ken tingim dispela lain - mekim olsem wanpela tok) MRK 5.8 +2 (em i olsem, skruim wanpela lain long paragraf long Mak 3.20) (long tok Inglis, expand the para at Mark 5.8 by two lines) MRK 6.23 +1[2] (expand the paragraph AFTER the paragraph which contains MRK 6.23 e.g. a heading.) Diglot AdjList i mas makim tu R o L bihain long buk kod na em i bikpela samting olsem L i kam paslain long R long wankain ves. MATL 3.4 +1 MATR 3.4 -1 MATR 3.11 +2 Keyboard Shortcuts: Ctrl-1 - mekim dispela lain nau +1 Ctrl-2 - mekim dispela lain nau namba 2 para +1[2] ... etc ... Ctrl-9 - mekim dispela lain nau namba 9 para +1[9] Ctrl-I - krungutim dispela lain nau -1 Ctrl-Grave - ` wankain olsem antap Ctrl-0 - % Comment (o uncomment) the line [it toggles] Ctrl-Comma - wankain olsem antap Ctrl-D - Duplicate the current line Ctrl-L - delete the current line Ctrl-Up - move the current line up one line Ctrl-Down - move the current line down one line Tingim olsem ol i mas stretim ol paragraf long pinis taim olgeta narapela saiting i pinis. Sapos nogat, ating yu bai mekim gen."

