"and bound together as a unit. A signature\n"
"may be made up of multiple sheets.\n\n"
"If unsure, leave this setting at 0 to indicate\n"
"that the publication will not be bound \n"
"using separate signatures."
msgstr "Ol i save pasim ol pes bilong buk na putim ol tok long ol pepa bilong en. Sapos yu no klia, orait putim dispela namba olsem 0 bilong soim olsem yu no inap pasim buk na putim ol narapela narapela tok long en."

