#: temp.glade:37557
msgid "Pagination: Physical paper size"
msgstr "Ol pes: Piksa bilong pepa"

#: temp.glade:37560
msgid "If the required size is not displayed, then \n"
"just type the required page width and \n"
"height separated by a comma. \n\n"
"For example: 203mm, 330mm (Foolscap)"
msgstr "Sapos yu no lukim bikpela bilong pes, orait rait long mak bilong pes long mak bilong mak bilong pes, na katim mak long mak bilong pes."

