msgstr "Pajinim: Painim pepa bilong karamapim buk olsem PDF"

#: temp.glade:37741
msgid "This option is only available if Create Cover is\n"
"enabled on the Cover tab. Enable this option if\n"
"you plan to print the outer (wrapper) cover\n"
"separately from the book's content. This is often\n"
"the case if cardstock, or a colour cover is used."
msgstr "Dispela opsen i stap tasol sapos yu opim Create Cover long Cover tab. Optimim dispela opsen sapos yu laik prinim ol hap bilong en (wrapper) i stap wanpis long ol samting i stap insait long buk."

#: temp.glade:37765
msgid "Whether you need a simple booklet\n"
"or a more complex signature, these\n"
"options allow plenty of scope."
msgstr "Maski yu nidim wanpela liklik buklet o sampela narapela kain sain, yu inap mekim planti samting long dispela rot."

#: temp.glade:37768
