msgid "Compare PDFs: Only show pages with differences"
msgstr "Skelim ol PDF: Lukim ol pes tasol i gat ol narapela narapela senis"

#: temp.glade:37847
msgid "When comparing two PDF files the\n"
"resulting \"Diff\" PDF can get rather\n"
"large. This option reduces the size\n"
"of the PDF by not including any\n"
"identical pages. This also saves\n"
"time as you don't need to search\n"
"through a lengthy PDF to find\n"
"out what might have changed."
msgstr "Taim yu skelim tupela PDF file, dispela \"Diff\" PDF i kamap bikpela. Dispela opsen i save daunim bikpela bilong PDF long no gat wankain pes. Dispela i save lukautim taim bilong yu, long wanem, yu no nidim painim long wanpela PDF bilong save wanem samting i senis."

#: temp.glade:37869
msgid "Compare PDFs: "
msgstr "Skelim ol PDF: "

#: temp.glade:37873
msgid "Use this color to show anything\n"
"that has been added (or moved to\n"
"the current location) in the new PDF."
msgstr "Yu ken yusim dispela kala long soim ol samting yu bin putim long nupela PDF (o kisim i go long dispela hap nau yu stap long en)."

#: temp.glade:37878
