msgid "The PDF showing differences between the old\n"
"and the new contains images that make the\n"
"resulting file rather large. Use this option to\n"
"limit the number of \"Diff\" pages created.\n"
"This will also potentially speed up the process."
msgstr "Dispela PDF i gat ol piksa i mekim na ol pes i bikpela moa. Yu ken yusim dispela opsen bilong pasim namba bilong ol pes i gat ol narapela narapela pes."

#: temp.glade:38015
msgid "Compare PDFs: Maximum pages of differences to show"
msgstr "Kompareim ol PDF: Makim planti pes bilong ol narapela narapela pes"

#: temp.glade:38027
msgid "Show Max\n"
"Diff Pages:"
msgstr "Makim Maksim Diff Pes:"

