msgid "Compare PDFs"
msgstr "Skelim ol PDF"

#: temp.glade:38047
msgid "Create 'diff' to Compare PDFs"
msgstr ""

#: temp.glade:38051
msgid "Enable this option to generate a PDF showing the \n"
"differences between the current PDF and the \n"
"selected previous version (set on the Finishing\n"
"tab under 'Compare PDFs').\n\n"
"If any differences are found, it should open the \n"
"\"Diff\" PDF in the default PDF viewer.\n\n"
"Shortcut: Ctrl-R"
msgstr "Enable dispela opsen long kamapim PDF we i soim ol narapela narapela samting namel long PDF nau na dispela i bin makim bipo (setim long Finishing tab aninit long 'Compare PDFs'). Sapos ol i lukim sampela narapela narapela samting, em i mas opim \"Diff\" PDF long default PDF viewer."

#: temp.glade:38103
msgid "PDF output format (Screen, RGB, CMYK, B/W, spot)"
msgstr "PNG Output Format (Piksa, RGB, CMYK, B/W, spot)"

#: temp.glade:38108
msgid "Select the appropriate standard \n"
"for the output format to optimize\n"
"the PDF for its intended purpose.\n\n"
"Screen (fastest, no post processing)\n"
"Digital (smallest size, for local printing, PDF/X-4)\n"
"Print (for professional printers, PDF/X-1a:2003)\n\n"
"Note: Digital and Print comply with archive standard PDF/A-1b."
msgstr "Makim ol tok yu laik putim long ol piksa long en bilong helpim yu long yusim gut ol tok yu laik putim long ol piksa."

#: temp.glade:38138
msgid "Select the appropriate standard \n"
"for the output format to optimize\n"
"the PDF for its intended purpose.\n\n"
"Digital (smallest size, for local printing)\n"
